ca-Brave-New-World.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）</a>为即将到来的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/captain-america-brave-new-world"><em>美国队长：勇敢的新世界</em></a>写了一首新歌。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kendrick-lamar-gnx-review-3815647">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar） - “ GNX”评论：将仇恨变成可教的时刻</a></strong></li></ul><p>这是根据演员安东尼·麦基（Anthony Mackie）的说法，他在超级英雄电影中描绘了名义上的角色。在<a href="https://www.etonline.com/media/videos/anthony-mackie-reveals-surprising-connection-to-kendrick-lamar-exclusive-233738" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>今晚娱乐</em></a>的新采访中，他透露：“肯德里克为我的电影制作了主唱。”</p><p>麦基补充说：“希望这不应该令人惊讶！我首先在这里打破它。我很兴奋，伙计。他的手艺的美丽和掌握……”</p><p>拉马尔（Lamar）重返<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威电影宇宙（Marvel Cinematic Universe）</a>是他<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/black-panther-soundtrack-review-kendrick-lamar-2239076#:~:text=Curated%20by%20the%20critically%20and,the%20uninitiated%20scratching%20their%20heads.">在2018年的<em>《黑豹》</em>专辑</a>之后。说唱歌手策划了唱片，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-sza-all-the-stars-video-black-panther-film-marvel-2237360">用SZA贡献了热门歌曲“ All The Stars”</a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-kendrick-lamar-weeknds-black-panther-collaboration-2234815">在Weeknd为我祈祷</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" 