 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/song-hye-kyo-gong-yoo-cast-new-netflix-k-drama-show-business-3836457">Show Business</a> ,</em> set against the backdrop of the gritty 1960s and 1980s Korean entertainment industry.</p><p> The post<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/singles-inferno-renewed-for-a-fifth-season-by-netflix-3837561">&#39;Single&#39;s Inferno&#39; renewed for a fifth season by Netflix</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
